{"tid":1318502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政 府 想 警 察 先 死","createTime":"2019-07-15T03:00:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T04:18:12.000Z","uid":257736,"like":99,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"dd1ad09e4f2bb880d3a36a81ba917bd98e88b466","tid":1318502,"uid":257736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:00:32.000Z","msg":"經過 旺角、 上水、沙田 一役<br />\n唔通你地仲未明咩？<br />\n政府想你地死<br />\n派咁多<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">CID 去前線</span>[/size=3]<br />\n警察一死，佢就可以大造文章<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">獲取 輿論同情</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qZHGzjN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqZHGzjN.png&h=b1bbbc74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你地無必要<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">服從上司講既所有野<br />\n請你擺脫奴性</span></span>  <br />\n[size=5]<span style=\"color: red;\"> 你地覺得盧狗唔合理，<br />\n就應該自己保護自己，<br />\n自己企出黎靜坐、罷工<br />\n唔好 中政府既計<br />\n</span><span style=\"color: red;\">警察，罷工吧，冇必要犧牲自己呀</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EBYbb8w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEBYbb8w.jpg&h=027168ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"></span>"},{"pid":"10e9311032bb444b01a2e40b8b9a99049943247f","tid":1318502,"uid":38461,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:01:42.000Z","msg":"佢係想大家轉移視線去警民衝突到<br />\n大家唔好忘記五大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"949b0beafa2ee74cce866d2d622820344de5b8a4","tid":1318502,"uid":162567,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:07:20.000Z","msg":"林鄭想警察冇用，出解放軍"},{"pid":"5b9ab61f6985d690a77d40f72fe839072734bc44","tid":1318502,"uid":19285,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:07:30.000Z","msg":"要將佢地既惡事浸入社區<br />\n係屋村入面貼CCTVB不能讓你知道的事<br />\n令到佢地變過街老鼠<br />\n佢地為左份糧同面子, 會內部自己分化"},